        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[We scrapped HK news using CORS proxy and cheerio to feed live news from below news channels:]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>We scrapped HK news using <a href="https://cors-anywhere.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CORS proxy</a> and <a href="https://cheerio.js.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cheerio</a> to feed live news from below news channels:</p><p>我哋用咗<a href="https://cors-anywhere.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CORS proxy</a>同<a href="https://cheerio.js.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cheerio</a>去收集下面各新聞網嘅即時/焦點新閒：</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.hk01.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HK01/香港01</a></li><li><a href="http://www.takungpao.com.hk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ta Kung Pao/大公報</a></li><li><a href="https://www.stheadline.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sing Tao Daily/星島日報</a></li><li><a href="https://hk.on.cc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Oriental Daily News/東方日報</a></li><li><a href="https://news.mingpao.com/pns" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ming Pao/明報</a></li><li><a href="https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vision Times/看中國</a></li><li><a href="https://www.epochtimes.com/b5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Epoch Times/大紀元</a></li><li><a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Yahoo/雅虎</a></li><li><a href="http://www.hkcna.hk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HKCNA/香港新閒網</a></li><li><a href="https://news.rthk.hk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">RTHK News/香港電台</a></li><li><a href="https://news.hongkongmetas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HK Matters/香港新聞連線</a></li><li><a href="https://news.tvb.com/tc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TVB News/無線新聞</a></li><li><a href="https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gov News/政府新聞網</a></li><li><a href="https://www.wenweipo.com/immed/hongkong" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wen Wei Po/文匯報</a></li><li><a href="https://www.am730.com.hk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">am730</a></li><li><a href="https://news.now.com/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Now News/Now 新聞</a></li><li><a href="https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BBC News/BBC 新聞</a></li><li><a href="https://www.abc.net.au/news/chinese/china" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ABC News/ABC 新聞</a></li><li><a href="https://ici.radio-canada.ca/rci/zh-hant" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CBC Radio/加拿大新聞</a></li><li><a href="https://cn.nytimes.com/hk-taiwan/zh-hant/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NY Times/紐約時報</a></li></ul>]]></content>
